# Search — <%= appName %>

Full-text search via **<%= provider %>**.

## Environment

<% if (provider === 'elasticsearch') { -%>
```env
SEARCH_PROVIDER=elasticsearch
ELASTICSEARCH_URL=http://localhost:9200
SEARCH_INDEX=<%= appName %>
```
<% } else { -%>
```env
SEARCH_PROVIDER=meilisearch
MEILISEARCH_HOST=http://localhost:7700
MEILISEARCH_API_KEY=
SEARCH_INDEX=<%= appName %>
```
<% } -%>

## Usage

```typescript
import { search } from './src/platform/search/index.js';

await search.index({ id: '1', title: 'Hello' });
const hits = await search.search('hello');
```
